lead_paragraph: With five victories, Jonathan Byrd had such a productive PGA Tour career that spending any time on the developmental Web.com Tour never crossed his mind. His only stop in the minor leagues was in 2001, so long ago that it then was known as the Buy.com Tour.

headline.print_headline: Byrd Brings Positive Attitude to Minor Leagues of Golf
